column16: Jack Wilson grounds out, shortstop Jimmy Rollins to first baseman Ryan Howard.
Brian McCann called out on strikes.
Freddie Freeman flies out to right fielder Hunter Pence.
Brian McCann grounds out, second baseman Chase Utley to first baseman Ryan Howard.
Jesus Flores flies out to center fielder Shane Victorino.
Rick Ankiel grounds out to first baseman John Mayberry.
